# Inventory Demand Forecasting & MLOps Pipeline

An end-to-end machine learning pipeline for **demand forecasting and stock recommendations**, built on the M5 Forecasting Accuracy dataset (retail sales time series). The project covers the full MLOps lifecycle: data preparation, model training, experiment tracking, and containerized model serving.

## Features
- **Data preparation & feature engineering** for time-series retail sales data
- **Demand forecasting model** built with XGBoost
- **Experiment tracking and model versioning** with MLflow
- **Model serving via a REST API** built with FastAPI, running on Uvicorn
- **Containerized deployment** with Docker for production-ready serving
- **Monitoring** via Prometheus client metrics exposed by the service
- Efficient data serialization with PyArrow

## Tech Stack
Python · Pandas · XGBoost · FastAPI · Docker · MLflow · Prometheus · PyArrow

## Project Structure
inventory_forecast_mlops/
├── data/processed/       # Cleaned and feature-engineered datasets
├── notebooks/            # Exploratory data analysis and model prototyping
├── src/                  # Production code: API, data processing, model logic
├── Dockerfile             # Containerized FastAPI service definition
└── requirements.txt

